Author: FridgethatRidge
Text: Ya. if I wake up and I don't feel like utter shit, I'll make sure to drink a copious amount of coffee so that way I feel jittery and like I'm about to faint. It's really stupid but I feel like if I don't feel like I'm about to die at any given moment I'm "faking my ed". Idk I'm just dumb lol.
